This is very light Garage for showcasing your models in menus. It can be used as workshop also.
It works on all unity versions and tested on 2021.3
It is made in Built-in Render Pipeline so you don't have to worry about anything
AO is baked so only directional light is enough. which makes it very light weight
Scene already has assets placed so just put your model inside the room
